snippet.title: FPV Freerider - Quadcopter Racing Simulator
snippet.description:
Available for Windows PC, Mac and Linux :
http://fpv-freerider.itch.io/fpv-freerider

...and Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Freeride.Freerider

Also available on Steam (Windows/Mac) :
https://store.steampowered.com/app/854250/FPV_Freerider/

(The music in this video is one of my favorite songs from the classic skate movie Molecules of Motion. For the longest time I was unable to find out who the artist is, thanks to a friendly person here in the comments I learned that it's 'And I Know' by Incomplete Monday. If you are the author/owner of the song and wish that I don't use it, please let me know).
